    "description": "You are <strong>PETER SHORTS!</strong><br><br>Grilling on a Saturday afternoon, Peter is ambushed and captured by a top-secret agency, who seek to use his DNA for cloning experiments. Can you help Peter (and his newly-cloned brethren) escape?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE MAIN ADVENTURE</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> EXPLORE the facility in this Metroidvania beat-em-up hybrid<br></li><li> Find and K.O. rogue PETER CLONES, and let BUG take them to safety<br></li><li> P2 can join as BUG, who can drop egg-bombs and capture enemies<br></li><li> TRANSFORM after defeating BOSS PETERS<br></li><li> Take down the MAD SCIENTIST who took Peter from his grill!</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A multiplayer VS Mode with 25 playable Peters<br></li><li> A built-in randomizer (unlocked after collecting all diskettes)<br></li><li> Simple 2-button controls with fighting game mechanics, including a GUARD, PARRY, and AIR DODGE<br></li><li> A vibrant 2A03+FDS chiptune soundtrack</li></ul>",
